data.title: Pele Awards Winners
data.meta_description: Take a look at this years best in advertising and design in the State of Hawaii!
data.text:
Aloha and Congratulations In partnership with NMG Network, Eleven 17 Creative, and the Hawaii State Department of Education Career and Technical Education Department, our High School Pele Awards enters its 6th year of competition garnering 675 entries from Hawaii High Schools Statewide.

16 Hawaii-based advertising and design professionals helped us judge this year's competition.

This year's 2024 Best of Show High School Winner will receive a $1,000 Cash Scholarship from our presenting sponsors, NMG Network and** Eleven 17 Creative as well as $2,500 per year Tuition Scholarship for 4 years to Chaminade University of Honolulu.**

We are proud to say that Hawaii has the only High School Program of its kind in the entire United States!

Aloha and Congratulations to all our 2024 High School Pele Award entrants, their teachers, and all finalists!
